  <brief_title>The Influence of Placental Drainage of Management of the Third Stage of Labor:a Randomized Controlled Study</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Istanbul Bakirkoy Maternity and Children Diseases Hospital</agency>
